[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 0.23"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes affect Tails 0.23.

We **strongly** encourage you to [[upgrade to Tails
1.0|news/version_1.0]] as soon as possible.

